summary: Quantum Cloak: A Quantum Secure & AI Enabled Privacy Layer 1 Blockchain - Quantum Cloak is a Layer 1 blockchain designed to provide the highest level of security and privacy through advanced cryptographic techniques such as quantum-resistant cryptography, zk-SNARKs, and Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE). The blockchain aims to develop a secure, scalable, and privacy-focused platform for digital transactions.
